WEBVTT

00:00:03.651 --> 00:00:04.851
Namaskar.

00:00:05.810 --> 00:00:08.290
Ja sam filmska zvezda, 51 mi je godina

00:00:09.588 --> 00:00:11.844
i još uvek ne koristim botoks.

00:00:11.868 --> 00:00:13.084
(Smeh)

00:00:13.108 --> 00:00:17.308
Dakle, čist sam, ali se ponašam, očito,
poput 21-ogodišnjaka u mojim filmovima.

00:00:18.468 --> 00:00:19.684
Da, radim to.

00:00:19.708 --> 00:00:24.604
Prodajem snove i širim ljubav
milionima ljudi kod kuće u Indiji

00:00:24.608 --> 00:00:26.904
koji smatraju da sam
najbolji ljubavnik na svetu.

00:00:26.908 --> 00:00:29.108
(Smeh)